==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɒtəl|-ɒtəl]]

===Noun===
'''wattle'''
#A [[construction]] of [[branch]]es and [[twig]]s [[woven]] together to form a [[wall]], barrier, [[fence]], or [[roof]]
#A [[wrinkled]] [[fold]] of [[skin]], sometimes brightly [[coloured]], [[hanging]] from the [[neck]] of [[bird]]s (such as [[chicken]] and [[turkey]]) and some [[lizard]]s
#Any of several [[Australian]] [[tree]]s of the [[Genus]] ''[[Acacia]]''
===Transitive verb===
'''to wattle'''
#To [[construct]] a wattle, or make a construction of wattles
